	.sr-only
		h3 Problem Space
		ol
			li
				p
					strong Prior knowledge
				h4 Lack of awareness
				ul
					li Not knowing what you're buying or consuming
					li Misinformation on substance effects, use and mixing
			li
				p
					strong Personal consumption
				h4 Oblivious use
				ul
					li Ignoring the role personal and biological factors play
					li Poor tracking and lack of awareness of consumption
			li
				p
					strong Emergency procedures
				h4 Poor assistance
				ul
					li Not knowing what to do in an emergency situation
					li Failing to get help - fear of asking or not knowing who to ask

