	.sr-only
		h3 User Segments
		h4 Regular Consumer
		p Users who consume drugs regularly and are looking for ways to do it more safely;
		p Looking to:
		ul
			li test their drugs to feel safer;
			li know what to do in emergency cases;
			li find safer places to buy from.
		p Uses the app more regularly to have a safer and more informed consumption.
		h4 John &lpar;Regular consumer&rpar;:
		ul
			li
				q I don't know if the drugs I buy are safe.
			li
				q Is it safe to have this kind of information on my phone?
			li
				q How will I know I'll get help if I need it?

