		h4 Information Seeker
		p Users who have friends or family who consume drugs and are looking to be more informed;
		p Looking to:
		ul
			li have more knowledge about drugs;
			li know hows to help their closed ones if needed, in case of emergency.
		h4 Cynthia &lpar;Information seeker&rpar;:
		ul
			li
				q I don't know what to do when my friends aren't feeling well at a party.
			li
				q Does this product have the information I need?
			li
